kja6ikirText: Brintellix® Pharmacokinetic Profile1
kja6ikisText:
The mean half-life of
Brintellix® is approximately
66 hours
kja6ikiuText:
Steady-state plasma
concentrations are typically
achieved within 2 weeks of
dosing Brintellix®
kja6ikivText:
The pharmacokinetics of
Brintellix® (2.5 mg to 60 mg) are
linear and dose-proportional
when administered once daily
kja6ikiwText:
The maximal plasma
Brintellix® concentration
(Cmax) after dosing is reached
within 7 to 11 hours post
dose (Tmax)
kja6ikixText:
Absolute bioavailability
of Brintellix® is 75%;
no effect of food on the
pharmacokinetics
was observed
